comments: Zeller (CHA) makes marginal contact to the body of Gordon (DEN) as he momentarily places two hands on Gordon's back while setting the pick. The contact does not affect his ability to defend.
Green (DEN) makes contact with Zeller's (CHA) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Campazzo (DEN) moves into Graham (CHA) and affects his SQBR, causing him to lose possession of the ball.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Graham (CHA) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Zeller (CHA) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by Gordon (DEN).
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Gordon (DEN) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Ball (CHA) makes contact to the arm of Jokic (DEN) as he secured the rebound.
Both Washington (CHA) and Harrison (DEN) engage in incidental contact while pursuing the loose ball.
Graham (CHA) commits a take foul on Rivers (DEN).
